          <div class="back News"><div class="featured-events-back-wrapper"><h3 class="featured-event-location"></h3><h2 class="featured-event-title">This week on our blog</h2><h4 class="featured-event-date"><div class="featured-event-day"></div><div class="featured-event-time"></div></h4><p class="featured-event-info">Since 2012 CARP has been implementing a wood turtle research and stewardship project. The overall goal of the Wood Turtle Monitoring and Stewardship project is to ensure the long-term persistence of the Wood Turtle and its habitat in the Annapolis River watershed.
Read more on our blog..
 
 
