          <div class="back News"><div class="featured-events-back-wrapper"><h3 class="featured-event-location"></h3><h2 class="featured-event-title">Kentville Library has moved! </h2><h4 class="featured-event-date"><div class="featured-event-day"></div><div class="featured-event-time"></div></h4><p class="featured-event-info">Kentville Lite is now open at 440 Main Street, lower level. Same hours and same phone number.
There is parking on site for our "Kentville Lite" location opening August 15. As well, here's a PARKING MAP from the Town of Kentville.
Please check back for further updates as we step into the next chapter for the Kentville Library.
AND! Margaret Atwood is supporting our new library with a Fundraiser for our Teen Area. You, too, can donate!
</p></div><a href="/news/kentville-library-has-moved" class="featured-event-link">Learn More <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></a></div>  			</div>
