          <div class="front News"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.valleylibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/featured_event/public/news-images/atwoodtile.png?itok=11H2cMOi" width="140" height="140" alt="" /><h3 class="featured-event-location"></h3><h2 class="featured-event-title">Margaret Atwood&#039;s Killam Corner</h2></div>    
          <div class="back News"><div class="featured-events-back-wrapper"><h3 class="featured-event-location"></h3><h2 class="featured-event-title">Margaret Atwood&#039;s Killam Corner</h2><h4 class="featured-event-date"><div class="featured-event-day"></div><div class="featured-event-time"></div></h4><p class="featured-event-info">The Kentville Friends of the Library, with the help of Margaret Atwood (!!!), are raising funds for the Young Adult area of the new Kentville Library. Find out how you can contribute by visiting the CanadaHelps page.
</p></div><a href="/news/margaret-atwoods-killam-corner" class="featured-event-link">Learn More <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></a></div>  			</div>
