          <div class="back Event"><div class="featured-events-back-wrapper"><h3 class="featured-event-location">Wolfville Memorial Library</h3><h2 class="featured-event-title">La Leche League Breastfeeding  Support Group</h2><h4 class="featured-event-date"><div class="featured-event-day"><span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2016-09-14T10:00:00-03:00">September 14th (Wed)</span></div><div class="featured-event-time"><span class="date-display-single"><span class="date-display-start" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2016-09-14T10:00:00-03:00">10:00am</span> to <span class="date-display-end" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2016-09-14T12:00:00-03:00">12:00pm</span></span></div></h4><p class="featured-event-info">This drop-in, Mom to Mom, breastfeeding support group offers a chance to meet other moms and babies in a casual comfy atmosphere.  A La Leche facilitator will be on hand to help answer any questions. The group will meet the second Wednesday of each month.
</p></div><a href="/event/la-leche-league-breastfeeding-support-group-1" class="featured-event-link">Learn More <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></a></div>  			</div>
