<div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-views-panes pane-nodequeue-2-panel-pane-1 featured-titles-wrapper"  >
  
        <h2 class="pane-title">
      New Adult Fiction Books    </h2>
    
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <div class="view view-nodequeue-2 view-id-nodequeue_2 view-display-id-panel_pane_1 view-dom-id-5a07b82da97fe3b82d6d85d938dbc136">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
        <div class="featured-title clearfix">
      
          <div class="field-content featured-book-image"><a target="_blank" href="https://avrl.catalogue.library.ns.ca/Record/1279256"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://www.valleylibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/featured_title/public/book_images/BookMatters.jpg?itok=YWfmwPGE" width="87" height="133" alt="" /></a></div>    
          <h4 class="book-info">Adult Fiction Books</h4>    
          <h2 class="field-content featured-book-title"><a target="_blank" href="https://avrl.catalogue.library.ns.ca/Record/1279256">The book that matters most</a></h2>    
          <p class="field-content featured-book-author">by Ann Hood</p>    
          <p class="field-content">Ava's twenty-five-year marriage has fallen apart, and her two grown children are pursuing their own lives outside of the country. Ava joins a book...</p>    </div>
  <div class="featured-title clearfix">
      
